[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering object serialization**\n\nI'm thinking about how the inner `out.writeObject(this.getEncoded())` might pass an object replacement that could affect things. If `BCFalconPublicKey.readObject` calls `in.readObject()`, it returns an `EncodedPublicKey` resolved to a byte array. It seems other tests, like those for `BCBIKE`, may have used this due to the Native Image serialization of byte arrays. I wonder how that impacts the broader context here.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0f7c9a8476518235016a26229174e4819786c1962d085efd18\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJiKoZ9DY6EKJd_1EQKtYPP7EiP8YizMynWCeOKDNFhce6_KQQEaIY-K2drlK8YgnUV22Y60zDOTYxydpIeFyMtQuyFVLRXdpU7Cc8wWFJ8L8A3aXX7Vhr_pBLfI2oeOkB8Kr1WGU9Gi5Arsa6iwJ9AXNLlyz-zh-gAt0sjvNU1xxCQrss4KccC7nrRe6-I58djJeAu191exKcYtOrntkVj4dl5v5xK2zQGWaDOYpMWjMI4ZVlXGO5PcFPj74JCF8ry7ezujKW0DRGOLRWR_NwjIBcNsdEVYHk2J9nojHA2mhmaUoJTIgzGDN2mqReg3AITiXzViGswtvsYxm02TyVRpSzDKE0r6GAMiG41M80iBcpgcSqHqmFrBgDXDG6wU4AE9SJDQ1B7OyY8SIP0xCX2nBF-EAQENXdAaDZzC5mIKrUpJuz5kCUO0a9jlPaM1AMMpLLXbEJaNJaXgXIEHsQxdjN6iszoL3lvhChF4etx8F_YBkBh3rchfYeKZc91u1nBmBTbBQKofGJi9LaDCFPMhqFeSlOIbAty35KWt0iu92XSE4SweCsta3nv9zEsfrDmCxr2kTZYXjxTcA8K4X5LSdgivRVKijYoegXQGEpjwLgLmV1A3_2oWhvSQfT6yV0WCJHwyZakQEjSbNr-kzvI_vt4-_W1kG4i4DNc-moty19r_hVcoW282XhCMEohig7IScgxEIQc2_Z8Kb6aYFnooqBBITaJu9fmgmDBIdmmmYWSxCTFnkg2kfRictHHwruVa-RRXP1UWKTOV-aewdoWG34IJ-lSnXEtEoketNjlqEx8h7VAL3_QexJZ8ows5ycMQuSuJNjoDPOCHZqNFMhucBUzk-BFJBRnTcmANRN9OSV2Gs-aTH-hgj3iRaw116kB5e6jSkkJNx15IeNQqbsvJa8FFmOQma3VnG-atn16ipTaKuCaliBDeivPbB4YHtTd_Ve0hqY9m_7p6gL0tkWQVCHTGkjUA_VhkBNrjN17cBNMQIHs1ItnCpMUlP8Ui8HRpK8rs6c9hVEr-y9hmz8MnYe7IIUUp3RZ-GcGu1wRK37MzJjV--ucLphR4eFXwHXbBOuIax8a5YAvFQPXO0F92ptryyMKqK8iwYQxvXnRcqi0f3CWd1Cn_9ZVnEuagwIbBvdKJ7Vzyahl4CWsl_pm7CgzUSYmNm3xatM8XA1G7KD8_wUYtHjkrbpJPR1LfyckWlmvXKam3nLDNNsH5NeK2m3Fbv9NBs1jkgaOMDWjb3B25Lukvv_XT